.TH SIMPLE_SHELL 1 "December 22 2023" "Version 1.0" "Holberton Simple Shell Manual"

.SH NAME
simple_shell \- a simple shell implementation
hsh - Holberton Simple Shell: command line interpreter

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B simple_shell
[\fIOPTION\fR]...

.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBsimple_shell\fR is a simple shell program that provides basic command-line
interpreter functionality.

.PP
\fBsimple_shell\fR reads user commands, interprets them, and executes the
corresponding programs.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h, \-\-help
Display this help message and exit.

.TP
.B \-v, \-\-version
Display the version information.

.SH COMMANDS
.PP
\fBsimple_shell\fR supports the following commands:

.TP
.B exit
Exit the shell.

.TP
.B env
Display all the variables in the environment.

.TP
.B \fIcommand\fR
Execute the specified command.

.SH ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
.PP
The following environment variables are used:

.TP
.B PATH
The colon-separated list of directories to search for executable programs.

.SH EXIT STATUS
.PP
.B simple_shell
returns a zero exit status on success, and non-zero on failure.

.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
To execute a command:
.BR simple_shell " ls -l"

